# ============================================================
# INVENTORY CORE RUNTIME
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: runtime
domain: inventory
scope: inventory.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for inventory.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers stock visibility,
reservation state,
movement state,
depletion state,
historical inventory reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- inventory context must resolve
- item/holding basis must resolve
- movement/reservation/depletion scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid inventory context
- invalid holding basis
- invalid movement scope
- invalid depletion path
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish stock state,
reservation state,
movement state,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- inventory runtime scope is explicit
- stock-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
